items.title: Sources: Blue Jays, Estrada agree on extension
items.summary: Marco Estrada, who had been on track to become a free agent after this season, has agreed to a one-year, $13 million extension with the Blue Jays, sources told MLB.com on Tuesday night. The club has not confirmed the agreement.
